data.description: The Eufaula Lake Home You've Been Waiting For Is Here! Just 2 miles to the #9 Marina, you're all set for the summer getaway you deserve.  Oh and wait until you see the improvements that are underway to connect your home to the prestigious Carlton Landing Community and all the amenities it offers! This lake home on a concrete slab foundation has all you need with a true 4 bedroom floorplan, generous laundry/utility/mud room, 2 car garage, fenced yard, and all appliances stay! You'll love that all bedrooms have convenient bathroom access and there's new carpet throughout!  Other upgrades and amenities include premium vinyl coated fencing, propane tank is owned, fresh interior and exterior paint, and garage door lift.  No crawlspace here with No maintenance worries with new roof and decking to be completed before closing.  What will you do with all the space available for a shop or garage for all the lake toys?  Just minutes east of downtown Eufaula offers convenient access to restaurants and shopping and only 2 blocks to Hwy 9 makes and easy commute to anywhere!  Put this one first NOW and end your lake home search!
